dekalog : nine ( polish : dekalog , dziewięć ) is the ninth part of the television series dekalog by polish director krzysztof kieślowski , connected to the ninth imperative of the ten commandments : " thou shalt not covet thy neighbor 's wife " . a man who has become impotent ( piotr machalica ) discovers that his wife ( ewa błaszczyk ) has a lover . ( a minor character in this film , a young singer with a heart condition , inspired kieślowski 's and piesiewicz 's next film , the double life of véronique . )